{"tid":2026838,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"XBox中国終被鎖區：中国玩家從此圍爐玩手指","createTime":"2020-05-21T08:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T08:53:55.000Z","uid":141060,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f180541bb0edd8de886d34f34058a53bcb5d96","tid":2026838,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=i%2Eibb%2Eco%2FX7zLxwP%2Fxi%2Dbox%2Ejpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=i%2Eibb%2Eco%2FX7zLxwP%2Fxi%2Dbox%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Di%252Eibb%252Eco%252FX7zLxwP%252Fxi%252Dbox%252Ejpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Di%252Eibb%252Eco%252FX7zLxwP%252Fxi%252Dbox%252Ejpg&h=6a807995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼PSN因為一名中国「XBox狂迷」向審查當局舉報「PSN有漏洞能玩境外遊戲」，令PSN中国server被「篤灰攬炒」收皮，因果的力量真強大，XBox中国的伺服器最近更新，也被證實從此鎖區，害人害己屢應不爽，簡直有如齋舖門口一本本因果輪迴故事的情節。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在百度貼吧的玩家證實，在最新update中，XBox ONE的中国版在5月16日已經鎖服，最新版不能再切入香港server、無論斷電還是各種重啟切換方式都終告無效。而由此引伸，很多360的遊戲都無法再遊玩，只能玩少量經廣電審查上架的「合法遊戲」，一眾平時為国家吶喊助威崇揚專制的玩家終於求仁得仁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=i%2Eibb%2Eco%2FV2fzHYd%2Fimage%2Epng&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=i%2Eibb%2Eco%2FV2fzHYd%2Fimage%2Epng\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Di%252Eibb%252Eco%252FV2fzHYd%252Fimage%252Epng%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Di%252Eibb%252Eco%252FV2fzHYd%252Fimage%252Epng&h=c468e917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=i%2Eibb%2Eco%2FcDX887N%2Fimage%2Epng&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=i%2Eibb%2Eco%2FcDX887N%2Fimage%2Epng\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Di%252Eibb%252Eco%252FcDX887N%252Fimage%252Epng%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Di%252Eibb%252Eco%252FcDX887N%252Fimage%252Epng&h=1a8e615b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中国近年的遊戲審查漸趨嚴格，一來是當局對流行文化的快速發展企圖納入掌控，而遊戲既是產業又引伸全新社會問題，更因為各式遊戲自由向外連結的國際服，正正是中国無法控制的國際通訊程式。所以由online game到主機遊戲，控制都漸見嚴苛。<br />\n<br />\n對非中国的玩家而言，將一堆外掛小粉紅封印回牆內，這絕對是連串好消息，但香港人不要鬆檞，不努力爭取自由的話，同樣的哀鴻也隨時在港服遍野。<br />\n<a href=\"https://gank.fanpiece.com/will-kuso/XBox%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%B5%82%E8%A2%AB%E9%8E%96%E5%8D%80-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%BE%9E%E6%AD%A4%E5%9C%8D%E7%88%90%E7%8E%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%87-c1376579.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgank.fanpiece.com%2Fwill-kuso%2FXBox%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E7%25B5%2582%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%258E%2596%25E5%258D%2580-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BE%259E%25E6%25AD%25A4%25E5%259C%258D%25E7%2588%2590%25E7%258E%25A9%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%258C%2587-c1376579.html&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsS8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=1eba0b8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gank.fanpiece.com/will-kuso/XBox%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%B5%82%E8%A2%AB%E9%8E%96%E5%8D%80-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%BE%9E%E6%AD%A4%E5%9C%8D%E7%88%90%E7%8E%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%87-c1376579.html</a>"},{"pid":"edfe095da75b3581414c29903be567e7286f22e6","tid":2026838,"uid":127751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打飛機啦大陸仔"},{"pid":"7d3f66adc8b27bc9b495549ea9a9ac973807219a","tid":2026838,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/yEY7nxa.png\" /><br />\n牆是好東西"},{"pid":"6382a9c7be7cd00c8addeefb8d29a80fa952abbc","tid":2026838,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:37:56.000Z","msg":"求幫推<br />\n[香港文化] 上連登打正字<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2026832